[00:09:43.520 --> 00:09:47.760]  Then he left the crowds and went into the house
[00:09:47.760 --> 00:09:51.040]  and his disciples came to him saying
[00:09:51.040 --> 00:09:55.200]  Explain to us the parable of the weeds in the field
